org.apache.iceberg.actions.RewriteFileGroup
public class RewriteFileGroup extends RewriteGroupBase<RewriteDataFiles.FileGroupInfo,FileScanTask,DataFile>
Container class representing a set of files to be rewritten by a RewriteAction and the new files which have been written by the action.
